\par \pard\plain \s253\li120\sb120\sa60\sl-240 \b\f25\fs20\lang1033 Overview
\par \pard\plain \s10\li120\sl-240 \f25\fs20\lang1033 {\b Net Gomuku}
 is a Network DDE version of the classic game of Gomuku.  Network DDE is part of Microsoft Windows for Workgroups version 3.1. Network DDE is not available in the standard Microsoft Windows version 3.1 operating system.
\par \pard\plain \li120\sb80\sl-240 \f25\fs20\lang1033 
\par For those who do not have Network DDE, {\b Net Gomuku} can be played against the computer.  However, the computer is a stupid player that only randomizes its moves.
\par 
\par Gomuku is also known by the names "Five in a Row" and "Pente."
\par 
