\par \pard\plain \li120\sb80\sl-240 \f25\fs20\lang1033 
Selecting this option causes the computer to randomly place your pegs for you.  Why you might want to do this I don't know.  I just put it in for debugging purposes.  With this option you can play over network DDE against an opponent who picks holes at ra
ndom, pit a random player against a random player over network DDE, or have the computer's random player play against your random player.  Boy, what fun!
